{"tid":988641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚇死人！男大生下體長「三顆睪丸」　醫師急喊：處理掉","createTime":"2019-01-20T08:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T12:46:52.000Z","uid":87540,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"57e39bb0d17bba7b18b5b0b274a1a73bbe70e36b","tid":988641,"uid":87540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:54:06.000Z","msg":"生活中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n一名大一的男學生，不慌不忙的走近泌尿科診所求助醫師，說明自己從開完疝氣手術後，右邊陰囊就長出一顆睪丸，現在一共有「三顆睪丸」，對此感到相當疑惑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/06/21/946363-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F946363-XXL.jpg&h=041741ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臉書粉絲專頁「小港高美泌尿科診所」發文，張醫師分享門診經驗，她說有一位長像英俊的大男孩來求診，詢問她「一個男人應該有幾顆睪丸？」張醫師回答「當然只有兩個」，但是男孩接著質疑，「那我為什麼從去年開完疝氣以後，我右邊陰囊又慢慢長出來一個睪丸？」張醫師拿起陰囊超音波對這「三顆睪丸」進行檢查，才發現其中一顆睪丸是「裝水的丸子」，男還得知後大失所望。<br />\n<br />\n張醫師解釋，「應該是術後小復發，或是組織受到剝離而形成的組織液堆積，醫療上稱為『陰囊水腫』。」<span style=\"color: red;\">男孩聽完後感到失望</span>，想要將其保留下來，不過張醫師認為，如果之後變成「大丸子」的話，還是建議處理掉比較好，避免因為擠壓影響睪丸的功能，讓健康出現問題。（編輯：黃雅琪）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2019/01/20/1547978972_16714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2019%2F01%2F20%2F1547978972_16714.jpg&h=70bab62a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪失望冇得問人同佢加埋有幾粒睪丸笑話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b652c4541b3fc903924f8556f911088e4f8874ef","tid":988641,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"單丸都夠啦 3丸冇意思"},{"pid":"12fe0ad406b6826b7c4284451565a6a36995e271","tid":988641,"uid":60527,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:56:49.000Z","msg":"終於搵到醫神跌落台既幕後黑手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff529bff193afbef630e7b2ecefd3454ceb836ec","tid":988641,"uid":215376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b652c4541b3fc903924f8556f911088e4f8874ef","tid":988641,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"單丸都夠啦 3丸冇意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:57:03.000Z","msg":"三咪單數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec938b26d80be8ba02fee42294df0c1a79c8284","tid":988641,"uid":9867,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:57:20.000Z","msg":"捐比Eason<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e578e35bdce688fafb1c60eea26b291da6df548a","tid":988641,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5ec938b26d80be8ba02fee42294df0c1a79c8284","tid":988641,"uid":9867,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:57:20.000Z","msg":"捐比Eason<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:58:42.000Z","msg":"入黎就想睇依句野"},{"pid":"97e572857a760747942e0ffe0d3ba34f04a8a359","tid":988641,"uid":48064,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"同組有條撚樣第一輪發言 一開始就話<br />\n<br />\n其實我天生有三粒睪丸 <br />\n一聽到呢度全組連考官都忍唔住笑左出黎 <br />\n<br />\n之後條撚樣繼續講話<br />\n但係我一直都唔敢同身邊既朋友講 收收埋埋左十幾年<br />\n就係dse開始前既study leave<br />\n我終於忍唔住要同我最好既朋友分享<br />\n但係我選擇用一個比較隱晦既方法去講<br />\n我同佢講 阿華 其實我同你加埋一共有五粒睪丸！<br />\n<br />\n阿華睜大雙眼望住我 驚呼<br />\n下！？ 乜原來你得一粒嫁渣 <br />\n<br />\n聽到呢度全組已經笑到收唔到聲 <br />\n<br />\n條友又開始講話 經過呢件事之後 <br />\n我終於發現到知人口面不知心呢個道理"},{"pid":"e0bfd356a1d8429cf35ad5fa39a233d842cd0fb1","tid":988641,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"3 cores"},{"pid":"54340bcc5b93a1f5cc221f99bad549f0962d08dd","tid":988641,"uid":86723,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:07:03.000Z","msg":"我同你加埋有五粒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吓 乜你得一粒"},{"pid":"8563460b8d18b3294ca93cdac31f8e0972d26b13","tid":988641,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97e572857a760747942e0ffe0d3ba34f04a8a359","tid":988641,"uid":48064,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"同組有條撚樣第一輪發言 一開始就話<br />\n<br />\n其實我天生有三粒睪丸 <br />\n一聽到呢度全組連考官都忍唔住笑左出黎 <br />\n<br />\n之後條撚樣繼續講話<br />\n但係我一直都唔敢同身邊既朋友講 收收埋埋左十幾年<br />\n就係dse開始前既study leave<br />\n我終於忍唔住要同我最好既朋友分享<br />\n但係我選擇用一個比較隱晦既方法去講<br />\n我同佢講 阿華 其實我同你加埋一共有五粒睪丸！<br />\n<br />\n阿華睜大雙眼望住我 驚呼<br />\n下！？ 乜原來你得一粒嫁渣 <br />\n<br />\n聽到呢度全組已經笑到收唔到聲 <br />\n<br />\n條友又開始講話 經過呢件事之後 <br />\n我終於發現到知人口面不知心呢個道理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T10:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街仔"},{"pid":"b83a209dffed68276b1c58b3969c0f09a9ff5a40","tid":988641,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"長相英俊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圖呢？"},{"pid":"96a64f3a426adca3f12fee1de5aafba9dc8f1a80","tid":988641,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b83a209dffed68276b1c58b3969c0f09a9ff5a40","tid":988641,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"長相英俊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圖呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T10:33:02.000Z","msg":"胯下大物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32123dcc50477b6782a8bb221ef9384fbc8be24b","tid":988641,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:46:52.000Z","msg":"疝氣係咪絕症，會不斷翻發"}]}